title: Ebro In The Morning - 2021 Summer Jam Lineup + Special Guest: H.E.R.
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/24.

Musical superstar H.E.R. joins the program to promote her new album (12:00 & 41:00), Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments (8:00, 59, & 1:37:02), and the crew discusses the Shared Pet Custody (1:11:00).  

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
